🔴 7. DSA — TREE TRAVERSAL (REAL USE)
🧠 Why Trees?

👉 Strategy rules can be represented as decision trees

🔥 Example Logic
          Price?
         /      \
     <3000      >3500
     BUY         SELL
🔹 Node Structure
class Node:
    def __init__(self, condition, left=None, right=None):
        self.condition = condition
        self.left = left
        self.right = right
🔥 Traversal (Decision Evaluation)
def evaluate(node, price):
    if not node:
        return None

    if node.condition(price):
        return evaluate(node.left, price)
    else:
        return evaluate(node.right, price)
🧠 Types of Traversal
Preorder → decision flow
Inorder → sorted logic
Postorder → dependency resolution
